column5: You found a good spot here!  they are Huge on pictures-forewarned is forearmed..lol!  welcome aboard  ID1
From one newbie to another, welcome.  Jackel

hello everyone,  been lurking around here for quite a while,  and it's been great to see how everybody helps everyone out.  i have learned alot from reading all of your posts and i would like to thank all of you   (now if i could only find the time to go fishing as much as i like to  )  i look forward to posting my reports and continue reading all of your great reports and becoming a proud member of this great community.     Peps
Welcome aboard

Hey there Peps!  Glad to see you came out of the lurking forest and that you posted an intro.  This is a great community...as you no doubt have already seen.  What kind of fish do you target?  What areas do you like to fish?  I'm know...being nosy....LOL.
Welcome, thanks for the intro...
Welcome aboard
Welcome Peps!  Jen

welcome aboard I hope you find it a nice place to lie about fishing, we do  oh and ignore the thing that states you can't see it because you don't have enough post or blocked......that's a joke in my signature ..well I think it's funny...LOL

thanks for the kind words everybody,  lie who's lieing  ccmt, i will fish for pretty much anything but pike and bass are my favourite.  fish parry sound area muskoka and want to really give simcoe a go this year.  gotta new boat last summer and didn't get it wet enough if you know what i mean.    Peps
Welcome Peps, I just joined the other day after trying for a while and I already feel like one of the gang so I am sure you will too in no time.  Looking forward to reading your reports.
welcome aboard
Welcome to the board!  Easton
Welcome aboard dude!!
no lurkers welcomed, haha, kidding  welcome...
Welcome to the zoo Peps. but be careful, it can be addictive.  Maureen
Welcome aboard.

Welcome to the board Peps, I too enjoy fishing the Parry Sound area for Bass and Pike. Discovered Crappie in my favourite lake so will be heading back up on the long weekend (hope the water is warm enough!)  Enjoy the zoo
Welcome to the board... Enjoy it as much as we do!!!
aaaaaaaaaaaaaa *Fishfarmer* welcomes you D (Board) have fun *Peps* aaaaaaaaaaaaa
Welcome Peps.......not everyone around here is a cranky as they sound.
Yes we may bark at times,but the bite is nothing to worry about.  Terry LIES all the time about his catch,s.  Welcome
Welcome Peps

Welcome aboard peps.   I kinda like some good pass and pike fishing myself.  Pass by the Georian Bay each year for our annual two week outing on the French.  Great country you have up there ... great country indeed.
Welcome on Peps. Hope you enjoy the camaraderie.
Welcome.Please send us lots of Pics
Welcome to the board, look foward to some good posts...
